-- Dubai’s Jumeirah to Manage Istanbul’s Historic Pera Palace Hotel
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-03-14T15:14:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-14/dubai-s-jumeirah-to-manage-istanbul-s-historic-pera-palace-hotel.html
Jumeirah Group LLC, the hotel-
management company that operates Dubai’s sail-shaped Burj Al
Arab, will start operating Istanbul’s historic Pera Palace
Hotel, said  Turkey ’s  Demsa Group , owner of the hotel.  Jumeirah and Demsa plan to hold a news conference March 19
to give details of the project, according to an e-mailed
statement from Demsa, a luxury fashion company that has
franchise rights to brands including  Harvey Nichols .  Pera Palace Hotel was built in 1892 in Istanbul’s central
Pera district to accommodate passengers on the Orient Express,
according to its  website.   To contact the reporters on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
